				\begin{document}$$\ddot{o}$$\end{document}dinger equation has been the target of many investigations by using integration strategies, analytical methods, and numerical schemes. Some other new methods which can be applied recently to the paraxial nonlinear schr\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
